# Spec-driven development

- **Source of truth:** `docs/SPEC.md` (section numbers are stable references in commits and PRs).
- **Before coding:** Identify the spec section (e.g. §4.4 prepayment policies) and implement only what it requires.
- **After behaviour changes:** Update or add **Vitest** tests; add or refresh **golden JSON** under `src/test/fixtures/` when §10 applies.
- **Non-goals:** Do not implement items in §11 without first updating `docs/SPEC.md` and `README.md`.
